robowars
Class HitRobotEvent

java.lang.Object
  robowars.AbstractEvent
      robowars.HitRobotEvent
public final class HitRobotEvent
extends AbstractEvent

Represents robot hitting a robot. An object of this class is passed to the event handler routine onRobotHit The conventions regarding axes and angles are the same as in Robot.
